{"tid":1253841,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[純宣洩] 其實對住廢中廢老嘅言論唔會嬲 反而好心痛","createTime":"2019-06-23T19:34:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-24T03:06:43.000Z","uid":30506,"like":97,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"c310753659326eea49d0fbf77f93e1f164408100","tid":1253841,"uid":30506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T19:34:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eDvJU0Z.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeDvJU0Z.png&h=1713a110&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢哋讀書唔多 但反而話大學生讀屎片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢哋經歷過文革嘅恐懼 但又痛罵為香港發聲嘅專業界別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢哋唔認識香港政治 甚至唔知道選民係需要登記<br />\n<br />\n但佢哋憑咩覺得自己睇穿全球政局 憑YouTube trending片？憑TVB灌輸嘅資訊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n喺香港生活過嘅人就會聽過中國大陸各種嘅不是 點解佢哋可以視而不見 仲要擁抱中國 甚至擁抱黨<br />\n<br />\n既得利益者要維護中共我明 但點解揸住身份證嘅阿叔阿伯要爭住認中國人 究竟邊個先係身在福中不知福<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港最容易被煽動嘅一班人 卻話另一班人被某某煽動<br />\n<br />\n我唔想嬲 嬲係冇用 但要改變 雖然改變好難<br />\n<br />\n有冇人可以話我知 除咗一笑置之以外 有啲咩可以幫到呢班廢中 令佢哋醒？"},{"pid":"b197017ca1fd1a877f67b1ee0232b28901575250","tid":1253841,"uid":30506,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T19:42:18.000Z","msg":"好似我上面cap 嘅一個留言咁<br />\n佢哋會覺得民生（電話俾錢好撚方便為例））就係一切 <br />\n即使犧牲法治、立法程序都冇所謂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁呢一切嘅諗法係因為泛民唔識玩政治？<br />\n定係因為受到某啲傳媒嘅影響<br />\n有冇廢中可以答到我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b67b573084cdc09a62a7cc7a580323d12ba844a8","tid":1253841,"uid":264780,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T19:52:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我係一個超紅底家庭出世 你問我答<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/PmjqdU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/PmjqdU</a>"},{"pid":"da4b598930b86b43652cf4eec82052906b31bd87","tid":1253841,"uid":6142,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T19:53:17.000Z","msg":"一切都係佢地班社會寄生蟲冇讀過書既錯"},{"pid":"abd8a604368b1c59f302a69faa04d0c53c233499","tid":1253841,"uid":78947,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T19:54:36.000Z","msg":"社會需要市井之徒，如果唔係去餐廳就冇人捧餐了"},{"pid":"dab637d6dcef2280169fc7110c7ec3fe4e928661","tid":1253841,"uid":30506,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T19:56:21.000Z","msg":"見夜媽媽冇乜人 分享一下家父對於612嘅睇法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n縱使佢支持修例 佢都覺得69遊行冇乜所謂 各有各發表<br />\n但一講起612就起晒鋼 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />無論有咩意見都唔應該衝擊立法會 佔領馬路<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁班示威嘅可以點做<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />應該照和平理性嘅方式<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />用晒喇喎 成百萬人（佢心目中幾十萬）遊行喇喎 仲可以點<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁都唔應該做違法嘅事 有咩咪坐低慢慢講<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁仲有咩和平嘅方法<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我唔知啦 總之咁樣就唔啱啦<br />\n<br />\n我心諗咁即係冇辦法啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n隔岸觀火有幾難 更何況其實啲火係燒緊落每一個香港人到 只不過我老竇唔知 唔識<br />\n<br />\n最慘係咩呀 係覺得自己識諗過你<br />\n唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23450627c904b3e416ebb666a727e5c79f445935","tid":1253841,"uid":30506,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"da4b598930b86b43652cf4eec82052906b31bd87","tid":1253841,"uid":6142,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T19:53:17.000Z","msg":"一切都係佢地班社會寄生蟲冇讀過書既錯"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T19:58:36.000Z","msg":"冇讀過書最多都係要挨窮啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj