lyTime":"2019-06-23T20:37:59.000Z","msg":"用電子嘢係方便監控咋"},{"pid":"cd6e11f69701e92be3dfa30cc7f2b2eb34dee63a","tid":1253841,"uid":30506,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"206bc8b51839853874507b0256147e41483a0238","tid":1253841,"uid":75028,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"dab637d6dcef2280169fc7110c7ec3fe4e928661","tid":1253841,"uid":30506,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T19:56:21.000Z","msg":"見夜媽媽冇乜人 分享一下家父對於612嘅睇法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n縱使佢支持修例 佢都覺得69遊行冇乜所謂 各有各發表<br />\n但一講起612就起晒鋼 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />無論有咩意見都唔應該衝擊立法會 佔領馬路<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁班示威嘅可以點做<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />應該照和平理性嘅方式<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />用晒喇喎 成百萬人（佢心目中幾十萬）遊行喇喎 仲可以點<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁都唔應該做違法嘅事 有咩咪坐低慢慢講<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁仲有咩和平嘅方法<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我唔知啦 總之咁樣就唔啱啦<br />\n<br />\n我心諗咁即係冇辦法啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n隔岸觀火有幾難 更何況其實啲火係燒緊落每一個香港人到 只不過我老竇唔知 唔識<br />\n<br />\n最慘係咩呀 係覺得自己識諗過你<br />\n唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T20:12:13.000Z","msg":"屌仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />啲對白exactly一鳩樣<br />\n佢地只係會諗表面嗰層 就係你班大學生阻民生<br />\n但無諗過係當權者處理有問題先迫到人行動升級<br />\n如果遊行就解決到問題 邊個想擺自己前途出黎玩命 <br />\n返去吃喝玩樂唔好<br />\n不過講到呢到<br />\n佢地又會話係外國煽動/入面有啲人收哂錢<br />\n<br />\n所以 屋企都係要避談政治 講黎哂鳩氣"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T20:38:43.000Z","msg":"諗起有篇文幾有趣 好值得形容呢班廢中嘅諗法<br />\n<img src=\"https: